quran[399]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"Naboola mbu: “ Murumilwe shina enywe Abarumwa ? ”"
  51,32,"Nibabola mbu: “ toto efwe khurumilwe khubandu abetsimbi.”"
  51,33,Khubalasile amachino keliloba
  51,34,Karebwakhwo eshimanyisio okhurula khu Nyasaye wo khulwa balia babura eshichelo
  51,35,Ne nikhurusiamwo Abasuubili balimwo
  51,36,Ne shikhwanyoolamwo halali inzu ndala yonyene yabasuubili
  51,37,Ne nikhulekhamwo eshimanyisio khubalia baritsanga eshinyasio eshilulu
  51,38,"Ne khulukano lwa Musa, olwa khwamuruma khu Firauni nende ebifune bilolekha"
  51,39,"Nakhola obufuru khumaanikeke naboola mbu, “ Oli Omulosi nohomba Omulalu”"
  51,40,Nenikhumutila nende omukanda kukwe kwabalwani nikhubasukuna munyanza naye nali ufunaanibwa
  51,41,"Ne (ukhusishibwa khwa) Abandu ba A’aad, olwa khwabarumila omuyeka omukumba"
  51,42,Shikwalekha shiosi shosi shiakwaburakhwo halali nikushikhola shinga likoshe
  51,43,"Ne Abandu ba Thsamudi, Olwa baboolelwa mbu: “ Musangale / mwikhoye khubise bititi”"
  51,44,"Ne nibakhaya okhulonda amalako ka Nyasaye wabu, mana likulu nilibakhupa nabo nibalola"
  51,45,Mana nibakhaywa okhwema ne nibalanyalilwa akhwihabina tawe
  51,46,"Ne Abandu ba Nuh imbeli eyo, toto bali Abandu aboononi"
  51,47,"Ne likulu khwaliumbakha khumaani nende obunyali, ne toto efwe khuli nobunyali obushila ako"
  51,48,"Ne liloba khwaliala, ne khuli abaali abalayi balibarie efwe"
  51,49,Ne buli eshindu khwaloonga eshisaatsa neshikhasi kho munyoole okhwitsulila
  51,50,"Mwilushile ewa Nyasaye, toto esie endi omwikanyilisi wenyu owahabulafu"
  51,51,"Ne mulameta khu Nyasaye, nyasaye wundi tawe, toto esie endi omwikanyilisi wahabulafu urula khuye"
  51,52,"Ne endio,shiyabetsela Omurumwa yesi yesi khubali imbeli wabu halali baboola mbu: “Oyo ni Omulosi nohomba Omulalu”"
  51,53,Ne koo baboolanila kano? halali bo ni Abandu abakhayi
  51,54,"Mana lekhana ninabo, nawe sholafunanibwa tawe"
  51,55,"Ne itsulisia, toto ametsulisio kakhoonyanga Abasuubili"
  51,56,Ne shindaloonga Majini nende Abandu halali khulwokhunaama esie
  51,57,"Ne Shebenyakhwo omukabo tawe, ne shindenya bandisie tawe"
  51,58,"Toto Nyasaye niye Omukabi, Owamani amanji"
  51,59,"Ne toto balia abamabii, bali nende tsimbi tsiabu shinga tsimbi tsia abaashiabwe. kho balayungubasia tawe"
  51,60,Ne eshinyasio eshikhongo khubalia bakhaya inyanga yabu yabalakwa
  52,1,Nditsuba khulukulu lwa Tur
  52,2,Nende khushitabu shiahandikwa
  52,3,Khuliseelo liabambulwa
  52,4,Nende khunzu yombakhwa
  52,5,Nende khushitsafu shiachingulwa
  52,6,Nende khunyanza yetsula
  52,7,Toto eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shilibaho
  52,8,Abulaho ulishikalila
  52,9,Inyanga yelikulu lilirenga okhurenga khwene
  52,10,Ne tsingulu lwatsilikulukha bukulukha
  52,11,Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubayingani
  52,12,Balia babayanga mumakhuwa kobusilu
  52,13,Inyanga yabaliluumwa mumulilo obutinyu
  52,14,"Baliboolewa mbu: “Kuno niko omulilo kwa mwaingananga.”"
  52,15,Koo buno ni obulosi nohomba shimulolangasa tawe
  52,16,"Injilemwo, mwifwile nohomba mukhaye okhwifwila ninashilala, toto enywe murungungwa kamwakholanga"
  52,17,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda nende mubwokholo
  52,18,"Nibasangalila khuka Nyasaye wabu abahele, ne Nyasaye wabu alibahonokosia khu shinyasio shiomulilo"
  52,19,Lie ne munywe mumwikhoyo khukalia kamwakholanga
  52,20,"Ne baliyekha khubifumbi bwoluyali, bilondokhane khulunyaali, ne khulibabashila Abakhana bomwikulu (Hurul ain)"
  52,21,"Ne balia basuubila mana olwibulo lwabu nilubaloonda khukhusuubila khulibabukanania, ne shikhulibalemilia khubikhole biabu shiosishiosi tawe, buli Omundu alirungwa shiayakhola"
  52,22,Ne khulibametela buli imbia yebiamo nende yeyinyama shingala benya
  52,23,Balihelesaniamwo tsigilasi tsilimwo eshinywebwa shibulamwo eshifwabi nohomba obwonooni
  52,24,"Ne Abakholi babu balibabotokhana, bang’enang’ena opara mbu ebisole bifunikhwe mugilasi"
  52,25,Ne balihengana nibareebana
  52,26,"Baliboola mbu: “Toto efwe khwali khale nabandu befu nikhwaria.”"
  52,27,"Mana Nyasaye nakhukhonya, nakhuhonia okhurulana nende eshinyasio shiomulilo"
  52,28,Toto efwe khwamulanganga Ye yenyene butswa. Toto ye niye omulayi wobukoosia
  52,29,"Kho yitsulisia, ne khutsimbaasi tsia Nyasaye wo sholi Omulosi nohomba Omulalu tawe"
  52,30,"Nohomba boboolanga mbu uno ni omukaasia wetsinyimbo, wakhulindanga lifwa limuulile"
  52,31,"Boola mbu: “Lindilisie toto esie siesi endi halala ninanyu mukhulindilisia.”"
  52,32,"Nohomba amaparo kabu niko kabarumanga kario, nohomba bo ni Abandu abafuru butswa"
  52,33,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “wakasia kano!” halali bo shibasuubilangasa tawe"
  52,34,"Mana barere amakhuwa shinga kano, nikali mbu baboolanga akatoto"
  52,35,"Nohomba shibaalongwa okhurula khu shiosi shiosi tawe, nohomba bo nibo baloonga"
  52,36,Nohomba nibo baloonga likulu nende eshialo? Halali babula obulaamba
  52,37,"Nohomba bali nende libishilo lia Nyasaye wuwo, nohomba nibo bali nobunyali"
  52,38,Nohomba bali netsingasi tsiokhurechelesiakhwo? mana omurechelesi wabu oyo arere ebifune bilolekha
  52,39,Nohomba Nyasaye ali nabakhana nanyu muli nabasiani
  52,40,Nohomba abarebanga bakhurunge nabo bali nende obuleemu bwo murungo oko
  52,41,Nohomba bamanyile akefisa mana bakahandika
  52,42,Nohomba benyanga okhukholela amatemo? Halali balia bakhaya nibo abalenjila mumatemo
  52,43,Nohomba bali nende Nyasaye wundi owulali Nyasaye? Nyasaye nomutswenufu khubia bamutsokasinjia ninaye
  52,44,"Ne nibalolanga lileesi lieshinyasio nilikwa okhurula hekulu, bakhaboolele mbu ni amalesi kachingane"
  52,45,Ne baleshe okhuula lwabalibukaanana nende inyanga yabu yabalisishibwa
  52,46,"Inyanga yamarechekho kabu shikakhabakhoonye shiosi shiosi tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe"
  52,47,"Ne toto balia abakhola amabii, balinyoola eshinyasio shindi shilali shino tawe, ne abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe"
  52,48,"Ne linda okhubusia khwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, toto ewe oli mutsimoni tsiefu, ne mutswenule khulwokhumwitsomia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olwa oba niwema"
  52,49,Ne eshilo khandi omwitsoomie nende olwe tsing’ining’ini tsitsia
  53,1,"Nditsuba\tkhu\ting’iningini\tolwa ikhamiukhanga"
  53,2,"Owashienywe\tuno shiyakora tawe nohomba shiyetsukhanila tawe"
  53,3,Ne shaboolanga khubwikombi bubwe tawe
  53,4,Halali ni obufimbuli bwafimbulilungwa
  53,5,Yechesibwa nende Owamani amanji
  53,6,Owakukhanga niyewotselesia
  53,7,Naye ali hekulu muno
  53,8,Mana owitsanga ahambi niyekha
  53,9,Naba hambi shinga akari wemikhono chibili nohambo ahambi muno
  53,10,Mana namufimbulila Omusumba we ubufimbuli
  53,11,"Omwoyo\tshikwaboola\tobubeyi khukakwalolo tawe"
  53,12,Koo mumuyingasinjia khukayalola
  53,13,Mana toto namulola khandi
  53,14,Mushisina shio musaala ( mkunazi) kwo khu malilikha
  53,15,"Ahambi nende omusaala oko, kuliwo omukunda kwamenywamwo"
  53,16,Olwa kwafimbwa omusaala oko nende shiakufiimba
  53,17,Tsimoni shitsiesundukha tawe nohomba shitsiabura eshichelo tawe
  53,18,Toto yalola ebimanyisio ebikhongo bia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi
  53,19,Koo mwalolakhwo Laata nende Uzza
  53,20,"Nende Manata, owundi wakhataru"
  53,21,Koo nenywe muli nabasiani Naye alinabakhaana
  53,22,Toto okho ni okhukaba okhubi
  53,23,"Ako namerasa kamwakulikha enywe nende basenywe, Nyasaye shiyeshiakhwo shiosi shiosi khumeera ako tawe. balondangasa amaparo nende shie mioyo chiabu chienya, ne toto abulunjifu bwabetsela okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu"
  53,24,Mbu Omundu anyoolanga shia yekombanga
  53,25,Nyasaye sa niye mwene eshialo nende mwikulu
  53,26,"Ne ni Abamalaika benga bali mwikulu, abokhusabila khwabu shikhulikhoonya yesi yesi tawe, halali khuwa Nyasaye achamile namufuchilila"
  53,27,Toto biala balasuubilanga mwikulu tawe balanganga Abamalaika amera keshikhasi
  53,28,"Ne babula shiabamanyile khu ako, balondanga butswa amaparo, ne toto okhuparirisia shikhukhoonyanga shiosi shiosi khubwatoto tawe"
  53,29,"Lekhana nende ulia uhelesia omukongo ametsulisio kefu, ne shiyenya shosi shosi halali obulamu bwokhushialo"
  53,30,"Awo naboolela khubumanyi, toto Nyasaye wuwo niye umanyile muno ulia wakora khunjila ye, naye amanyile muno ulia walunjikha"
  53,31,"Ne nibia Nyasaye biosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo, kho abarunge betsimbi khukabakholanga ne abakhola amalayi abarunge obulayi"
  53,32,"Balia beikalilanga okhukhola ebionono ebikhongo nende akeshifwabi, halali orwonono orutiti titi, Toto Nyasaye wuwo obulesheli bwe nobuunji, Ye abamanyile muno, olwa yabaloonga okhurula khuliloba , nende ngamwali mutsinda tsia banyinenywe, kho muleelole tawe, Ye amanyile muno owamuria"
  53,33,Koo! Walolakhwo ulia ufutariranga
  53,34,Nayinia shitutu mana niyemana
  53,35,"koo akhali nende obumanyi khu kefisile, mana alolanga"
  53,36,Nohomba shiyabolelwakhwo khukali mubitabu bia Musa
  53,37,Nende Ibrahim wosia indache
  53,38,Mbu Omundu shalichinga tsimbi tsiowashie tawe
  53,39,Ne Omundu shalinyoola halali kalia kayakhola
  53,40,Ne toto ebikhole bibie bililolekha
  53,41,Mana alirungwa omurungo kukwe kwosi
  53,42,Ne toto khu Nyasaye wuwo niwo akaliweela
  53,43,Ne toto niye ureranga okhutsekha nende okhulila
  53,44,Naye toto niye owufwisinjia nende ulamusinjia
  53,45,Ne toto ye niye waloonga eshisatsa nende eshikhasi
  53,46,Okhurulana nende imwo yolwibulo nimitswa
  53,47,Netoto mbu kali khuye okhulamusibwa khandi
  53,48,"Naye\tniye\tuyindiasinjia\tnende uhelasinjia"
  53,49,"Naye\tniye\tNyasaye\tOmuleli wetsing’ining’ini tsia (shiira)"
  53,50,Naye niye wasishia A’ad beimbeli
  53,51,Nende Tsamudi shibalekhwa tawe
  53,52,"Nende Abandu ba Nuhu abaliho imbeli, Toto bali ababii muno ebitsimbi po"
  53,53,"Nende tsingongo tsiakalukhanibwa, niye watsikalukhania"
  53,54,Nitsifuunikhwa nende biatsifuunikha
  53,55,Mana nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wuwo tsiokanakananga
  53,56,"Uno ni omwikanyilisi, mubekanyilisi beyimbeli"
  53,57,Inyanga yeyindukho ilihambi
  53,58,Owumao wakhaibuula owulali Nyasaye
  53,59,"Ne\tamakhuwa\tkano nikamwisundushilanga"
  53,60,Ne mutsekhanga ne shimulilanga tawe
  53,61,Nanyu muli mubukoyani
  53,62,Ne musujudile Nyasaye ne mumulaame
  54,1,"Indukho ilihambi, ne omwesi kwabuukhemwo"
  54,2,Ne nibalola eshimanyisio shiosi shiosi bashifutarira nibaboola mbu “ buno nobulosi butsilililanga”
  54,3,"Ne baingasia ne nibaloonda okhwenya khwabu, ne buli likhuwa liemekhwa"
  54,4,Netoto kamala okhuboolela amakhuwa kalimwo obwalaba
  54,5,"Amachesi kafung’anile, halali amekanyilisio shikakhoonya eshindu khubo tawe"
  54,6,Mana lekhana ninabo. Inyanga yalilaanga omulaanji okhutsiila likhuwa lio mwoyo kwakhaya
  54,7,"Tsimoni tsiabwe tsilihenga hasi, Balirula mubilindwa opara mbu nitsisiche tsisaalanibwe"
  54,8,"Nibelushila Omulaanji, ne Abakhayi baliboola mbu: “Inyanga ino ni indinyu.”"
  54,9,"Abandu ba Nuh bakhaya bo nibashili, nibayingasia\tOmusumba\twefu, nibamuboolela mbu nomulalu mana nibamwalabila.(nibamululila)"
  54,10,"Mana nasaba Nyasaye wuwe; naboola mbu: Toto esie ekhailwe, kho habine"
  54,11,Mana nikhwikula emiliango chomwikulu khu maatsi kayombokhanga
  54,12,"Ne nikhufutula liloba nikhukhola emialo (emichela), amatsi nikabukanana khulikhuwa liali niliburire"
  54,13,Ne nikhubachinga khushietsimbao nende imikoye. (Isafina)
  54,14,"Yatsitsanga nikhuyihenga, okhuba ni omurungo khu kalia kabamuingasinjia"
  54,15,"Ne toto bwene khwachikhola okhuba eshimanyisio, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,16,"kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie, nende okhwikannyilisia khwanje"
  54,17,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani ibe inyangu okhumanya, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,18,"Babu A’di bakhaya, kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje"
  54,19,Toto efwekhwabarumila omuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka khutsinyanga tsimbi tsilondokhaane
  54,20,Nikusiula Abandu opara mbu nebisichiri biemisala chisiulilwe
  54,21,Mana eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende amekanyilisio kanje
  54,22,"Netoto efwe khwakhola Ikurani ibe inyangu okhuyimanya, Ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,23,Abandu ba Thamudi bayingasia Abekanyilisi
  54,24,"Nibaboola mbu : “Khuloonde Omundu namundu urula mwifwe, efwe mana khuba khulaba mubokori bwahabulalu.”"
  54,25,Niye butswa yenyene okhurula mwifwe wamakanyiliso keshela ? halali uno nomubeyi omukhongo omufuru
  54,26,Nibamanye mutsuli niwina umubeeyi omukhongo omufuru
  54,27,"Toto efwe khwitsa okhubarumila ingamia ikhasi kulwa okhubatema, mana obahenge butswa mana wifwile"
  54,28,"Ne baboolele mbu amatsi kalakabulwamwo hakari wabu, balakabukhasibwa khulwa okhukanywa"
  54,29,"Mana nibalaanga Omundu wabu, niyetsa nayisinza"
  54,30,Ne eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie nende okhwikanyilisia khwanje
  54,31,"Toto efwe khwabarumila oluyoka lulala lwonyene, nibabashinga abitiisi biokhumbashila olukaka"
  54,32,"Ne toto efwe khwakhola Ikurani okhuba Inyangu, ne koo khuliwo nende witsulila"
  54,33,Abandu ba Lut bayingasia abekanyilisi
  54,34,"Toto efwe khwabarumila eshifulumutu shiamachina halali abaloondi ba Lut, khwabahabina mumabwibwi"
  54,35,"Tsimbabasi okhurulu khwifwe, Endio nilwakhurunganga ulia ukhupanga orio muno"
  54,36,"Ne toto yabekanyilisilia eshinyasio shiefu, halali bo bali netsinganakani khumekanyilisio ako"
  54,37,"Ne toto benya mbu abahelesie abacheni be, mana nikhubawofusia tsimoni tsiabu , nikhubaboolela mbu: “pile eshinyasio shianje namekanyilisio.”"
  54,38,Ne toto shiabeeshela eshinyasio shitsilila mumabwibi
  54,39,Kho mana pile eshinyasio shianje namekanyilisio
  54,40,"Netoto khwakhola Ikurani okhuba inyangu, ne koo khiliwo nende witsulila"
  54,41,Netoto Abekanyilisi betsela Abandu ba Firaun
  54,42,"Bakhaya ebimanyisio biefu biosi pe, mana nikhubatila omutilo kwa amaani kwobunyali"
  54,43,Ne Abakhayi benyu bali nende amani okhushila abo baranjilila nohomba kahandikwa mubitabu mbu enywe mubule okhufunaanibwa
  54,44,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: ‘‘efwe khuli abaanji khulishila butswa.’’"
  54,45,Abanji abo balashilwa ne balakalukha inyuma tsimbilo
  54,46,"Halali inyanga yeyindukho niyabalakwa, Ne indukho ni isiro muno mana khandi indulu pa"
  54,47,Toto Abetsimbi balimubukori nende mubulalu
  54,48,"Inyanga yabaliswerululwa mafumama nibasukunwa mumulilo, baliboolelwa mbu : ‘‘pile omulilo kwa Jahanam.’’"
  54,49,Ne toto buli eshindu khwaloonga khushichelo
  54,50,"Ne likhuwa liefu nililala butwa, shinga okhulimba no khulimbula tsimoni"
  54,51,Ne toto khwasishia abashienywe alikho mwinywe uparanga
  54,52,Ne koosi kabakhola kali mubitabu
  54,53,Liosi liosi lititi nende likhonga liahandikwa
  54,54,Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mwikulu mumikunda chilimwo emialo
  54,55,"Mushikhalo shiatoto, ewo Omwami Omunyali"
  55,1,Owetsimbabaasi tsinyinji
  55,2,Yechesia Ikurani
  55,3,Yaloonga Omundu
  55,4,Namwechesia okhuboola
  55,5,Eliuba nende omwesi bichendanga khubise
  55,6,Ne emilandula nende emisaala binamilanga Nyasaye
  55,7,Ne yachingula likulu naraho eshichelo
  55,8,Kho mulatutuyia eshichelo tawe
  55,9,Ne muchele habwene ne mulaleemia eshichelo tawe
  55,10,Ne liloba yaliraho khulwe ebiloonje
  55,11,Lilimwo ebiamo nende emitende chili nende ebibuli
  55,12,Nende imele yamakhoba nende - amasafu ka -raihan kawunya obulayi
  55,13,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,14,Yaloonga Omundu okhurula khwiloba shinga omuloonji wetsinyungu
  55,15,Ne naloonga Amajini okhurula khumulilo
  55,16,kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,17,Nyasaye omulesi we ebukwe tsibili nende we mumbo tsibili
  55,18,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,19,Achesinjia tsinyanza tsibili halala
  55,20,Hakari watsio khuliho nende eshikalilo tsilasasania tawe
  55,21,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu etsiamukhayanga
  55,22,"Mutsinyaanza etso\tebisole (lulu) birulangamwo nende ebiendo (marjan)"
  55,23,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,24,Ne bioosi ni ebibie bichendanga khumaatsi shinga tsingulu
  55,25,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,26,Bioosi bili khushialo biliwa
  55,27,Ne alitong’a Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi woluyali nende Amaani
  55,28,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,29,"Biosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo bisabanga Nyasaye, buli ebise atsililisinjia amakhuwa"
  55,30,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,31,Khulibarunga enywe emikanda chibili
  55,32,Ne nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,33,Enywe Amajini nende Abandu nimunyala okhunyeleela elwanyi welikulu nende eshialo nakhanyeleele. Neshimunyala okhunyeleela tawe okhula mufuchililwe
  55,34,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,35,"Mularumilwa tsinzesele tsiomulilo nende ebichuma bisaalululwe, mana shimulahona tawe"
  55,36,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,37,Olwelikulu liliatikha mana libe eliakhanyu shinga amafura mumulilo
  55,38,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,39,Inyanga eyo obulao ulireeba tsimbi tsitsie Omundu nohomba lijini
  55,40,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,41,"Abetsimbi balimanyikhana khubimanyisio biabu, nibatilwa khulwotosi nende ebisisilo"
  55,42,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wwenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,43,Ino niyo Jahannamu ya babii bayingasinjia
  55,44,Bakhabotokhanengemwo nende amatsi kamwo akayia pia
  55,45,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,46,Ne ulia waria okhwemibwa imbeli wa Nyasaye wuwe aliba nemikunda chibili
  55,47,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,48,Emikunda chilimwo emisaala chiamasaka amarakalafu
  55,49,kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
  55,50,Tsisebele tsilimwo tsibili tsikhulukusinjia
  55,51,Kho nitsimbabaasi shina tsia Nyasaye wenyu tsiamukhayanga
