  55,78,lihebwe oluyali elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Woluyali nende Obwani
  56,1,Olwe eshikhole shilikholekha (olweyindukho iliula)
  56,2,Abulaho uliyingasia okhwikholekha khwashio
  56,3,Shishinjia shinininjia
  56,4,Olwe eshialo shilirenjibwa obutinyu
  56,5,Ne olwetsingulu tsilisiebwa busiebwa
  56,6,Tsiabashinga olufu lutumukha
  56,7,Nanyu muliba tsimbia tsitaru
  56,8,"Abandu bomukhono omulunji, koo ni babu wina abo Abandu bomukhono omulunji"
  56,9,"Ne Abandu bomukhono omukaata, koo nibabu wina abo bomukhono omukaata"
  56,10,Ne beyimbeli baliba imbeli
  56,11,Abo nibo balibukanilwa
  56,12,Mumikunda chiomwikulu chobwokholo
  56,13,Omukabo omukhongo khubaali imbeli
  56,14,Nende mutiti khubeyinyuma
  56,15,Baliba khubifumbi biaronwa
  56,16,Baliyiekhakhwo nibalolana
  56,17,"Balikhalabanilwa\tnende\tAbasiani bolusoolili lulawa tawe"
  56,18,"Nibachinjile bikombe nende tsibinika nende tsigilasi, tsilimwo ebinywebwa okhurula musebele ingwalafu"
  56,19,"Shibilibatsunia\tomurwe\tnohomba shibilibamesia tawe"
  56,20,Nende ebiamo biabayanza
  56,21,"Nende\tinyama\tyeliyoni\tshingala bekombanga"
  56,22,Nende Abakhana bomwikulu
  56,23,Bali shinga ebisole bialiindwa
  56,24,Omurungo khukabakholanga
  56,25,Shibaliwulilamwo keshifwabi nohomba ketsimbi tawe
  56,26,Halali amakhuwa komulembe konyene
  56,27,"Ne Abandu bomukhono musatsa , nishina shilinyoola Abandu bomukhono musatsa"
  56,28,Baliba khumisaala chibulaho amawa
  56,29,Nende ebikoko biloondane
  56,30,Nende eshinikha eshikhongo
  56,31,Nende amaatsi kakhulukusia
  56,32,Nende ebiamo ebinji
  56,33,Shibiwetsanga nohomba shibikalilungwa tawe
  56,34,Nende obulili bwachingulwa
  56,35,"Toto efwe khulibaloonga\tabakhana bomwikulu (hurul ain) obuyia"
  56,36,Mana khulibakhola abashisila
  56,37,Bachamana nende Abasatsa babu abayelana ninabo
  56,38,Khulwa Abandu bomukhono musatsa
  56,39,Omukabo omukhongo khubaali imbeli
  56,40,Ne omukabo omukhongo khubaali inyuma
  56,41,"Abandu bomukhono mukhasi , koo ni shina shilinyoola Abandu bomukhono mukhasi"
  56,42,Baliba mumuyeka kwomulilo nende amatsi kayia pia
  56,43,Nende eshinikha shiomwosi omumali ti
  56,44,"Shishili shiokhunyoolamwo\tobunyifu nohombo obwihotselefu tawe"
  56,45,Toto abo bali khale awo bamenyanga shinga benya
  56,46,"Ne\tbaali\tnibakhaila\tkhubionoono ebikhongo"
  56,47,"Ne baboolanga mbu nikhumala khwafwa mana nikhuba liloba nende ebikumba, mbu toto efwe khulilamusibwa"
  56,48,Nohomba bapapa befu bakhale
  56,49,"Boola mbu: “balia abeyimbeli nende inyuma”"
  56,50,“Toto balilamusibwa khubise bieyinyanga yarechekhwa.”
  56,51,Mana toto enywe abakori abakhayi
  56,52,Mulilia toto omusala kwa zaqoom
  56,53,Mulikwitsusia mutsinda tsienyu
  56,54,Ne mana mulinywa amaatsi kayile pia
  56,55,Nemulikanywa shinga ingamia inywetsanga nili nende obuloo
  56,56,Ino niyo isambo yabu inyanga yomurungo
  56,57,Efwe khwabaloonga enywe shichilanga shina nimulasuubila
  56,58,Koo mulolangakhwo amatsi kolwibulo kamwitikhanga
  56,59,"Koo\tnenywe\tmukaloonganga nohomba nefwe abaloonji"
  56,60,Efwe khwabarecheshela lifwa nafu shikhushilungwa tawe
  56,61,Okhukalukhania abaandi balali enywe ne khubalonje enywe ebindi biamulamanyile tawe
  56,62,"Netoto mwamala okhumanya okhulongwa khwa ambeli, neshina shichilanga nimuletsulilaanga"
  56,63,"Ne\tmulolangakhwo\temimela chiamuraakanga"
  56,64,Nenywe muchimesinjia nohomba nefwe khuchimesinjia
  56,65,"Ne nikhwenya nikhuchikhola chiakhaya okhurakhwo shiosi shiosi, mwatong’a nimung’ang’alile"
  56,66,Nimuboola mbu toto efwe khusishile
  56,67,Halali efwe khwimilwe
  56,68,"Koo\tmulolangakhwo\tamaatsi kamunywetsanga"
  56,69,Ni enywe mukeshinjia okhurula mumaleesi nohomba nefwe bakeshiinjia
  56,70,"Nikhwenya nikhukakhola keyichumvi , ne shina shichilanga nimuloopa orio"
  56,71,Mulolangakhwo omulilo kwamwashinjia
  56,72,Nenywe mwaloonga omusaala kwakwo nohomba nefwe baloonga
  56,73,Efwe khwakukhola okhuba eshitsulisio nende kwokhukhoonya balia bali mushitsimi
  56,74,Ne witsoomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo omukhongo
  56,75,Netoto nditsuba khubise bietsing’ining’ini tsikwitsanga
  56,76,"Ne toto shino neshitsubo eshikhongo, mumanyangakhwo toto"
  56,77,Toto eyo ni Ikurani yoluyali
  56,78,Mushitabu shialindwa
  56,79,Shashitilangakhwo halali ulia Omutswenufu
  56,80,Sheshibwa okhurula khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi
  56,81,Ne kano namakhuwa kamulekanga
  56,82,Amwakhopele orio khumukabo kwenyu (kwa abahele) nanyu mwikhola mbu muyingana
  56,83,Kaliba karie olwa omwoyo kuliuula khulukamukamu? (Mwiporokotio)
  56,84,Ne enywe ebise ebo muhenganga
  56,85,"Ne efwe khuli ahambi muno ninanyu , nanyu shimukhulolanga tawe"
  56,86,Ne enywe mukhaya okhuba mubunyali bwanje
  56,87,mbu shina nimulakalusia omwoyo oko nikali mbu muboolanga obwatoto
  56,88,Ne naliba mubalibukanilwa
  56,89,Kuliba omwikhoyo nende eshing’ari nende emikunda chobwokholo
  56,90,Ne naliba mubandu bomukhono omusatsa
  56,91,Ni omulembe khwiwe owuli Mubandu bomukhono musatsa
  56,92,Ne naliba Mubuyingani Abakori
  56,93,Isambo yiyie niya amaatsi kayile pia
  56,94,Nende okhwinjisibwa mumulilo
  56,95,Toto buno nibo obwatoto bwokhwisikwa
  56,96,Kho witsoomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi Omukali muno
  57,1,"Bimwitsoominjia Nyasaye bili mwikulu nende mushialo naye niye Owamani, Owamachesi muno"
  57,2,"Nobubwe obwami bwo mwikulu nende khushialo, niwelesinjia obulamu ne niye ufwisinjia, naye ni omunyali wabuli eshindu"
  57,3,"Ye niye wokhuranga na niye wokhumalilikha naye niye owahabulafu nende owulalolekha, naye niye Omumanyi wabuli eshindu"
  57,4,"Niye woloonga likulu nende eshialo, khutsinyanga sita, Mana naleeng’ana khu shisaala, yamanya shinjilanga mwiloba nende shirulangamwo, nende shikholomokhanga okhurula mwikulu nende bininanga hekulu, Naye alininanyu wosiwosi wamuli. Ne Nyasaye alolanga muno kamukholanga"
  57,5,"Obwami bwo mwikulu nende khushialo nobubwe, ne ewa Nyasaye ni amakhuwa koosi kakalusibwa"
  57,6,"Yenjisinjia eshilo mushitere, ne yenjisinjia eshitere mushilo, naye niye umanyile muno kali mubilifu"
  57,7,"Suubile khu Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, ne murusie khubia Nyasaye yamukhola okhuba abalindi , Kho balia basuubila mwinywe, mana nibarusia baliba nende omurunga omukhongo"
  57,8,"Ne muli murie mula suubilanga khu Nyasaye ne Omurumwa abalaanganga, mbu musuubile khu Nyasaye wenyu, naye toto yamala okhubukula indache yenyu, toto nimuli abasuubili"
  57,9,"Ye niye wishilinjia omusumba wuwe tsinyaali tsinoosinjia, kho tsibarusie mushiilima nitsibeenjisia mubulafu, Ne toto Nyasaye khwinywe ni Omwihotselefu Owobukoosia muno"
  57,10,"Muli murie mularusinjia khunjila ya Nyasaye, ne nibiaNyasaye biosi bili khushialo nende mwikulu, shibali nashilala tawe owayiinia mwinywe nikhushili okhufungula Makka, mana nalwaana, abo bali nende omurungo omukhongo okhushila balia bayinia Makka niyikulwe, mana nibalwana, ne boosi Nyasaye yabalaka amalayi, ne Nyasaye amanyile koosi pe kamukholanga"
  57,11,"Ni wina wiwosia Nyasaye likofi lilayi, ne amurunge omurungo kumeteshe, ne anyoole omurungo kwobuhaani"
  57,12,"Inyanga yolilola abasuubili abasatsa nabakhasi, obulafu bwabu buli imbeli wabu, nende omukhono kwabu omusaatsa, omwikhoyo kwenyu lelo, emikunda chiburangamwo emialo , mulikhalamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, okho nikho okhubura okhukhongo"
  57,13,"Inyanga ya abishikhabili abeshisatsa nende abeshikhasi baliboolela abasuubili mbu: ‘‘mukhuliinde khunyoole okhulolela obulafu bwenyu.’’ lisisi lilirebwa hakari wabu lio muliango – mkari nikwetsimbabaasi na elwanyi nikweshinyasio"
  57,14,"Balibalaanga nibababoolela mbu: “Abayiee shikhwali ninanyu?” balibaboolela mbu: “Nabweene, halali enywe mwechemela abeene\tnimukanakana,\tnimuba neshibeyibeyi ne obwikombi bwe mioyo chienyu nibumukosia, okhula shingala Nyasaye wuwo abusiiye, mana omubeyi nababeya okhukhaya okhuloonda Nyasaye"
  57,15,"Toto nyanga ino sishilibukulwa shiosi shiosi khwinywe shokhubanunula tawe, nohomba balia abakhaya, eshimenyo shienyu ni mumulilo, nimwamukhoyeshele, ne amakalushilo amabii kamakana"
  57,16,"Ne koo ebise bishili okhula khubasuubila emioyo chiabu chihotselesie khulwokhwitsulila Nyasaye nende khulwa amakhuwa ka toto keshibwe? Ne balaba shinga balia abahebwa eshitabu bali imbile wabu, nibaba nende ebise ebirambi, imioyo chiabu nichiba emiumilano, ne obunji bwabu nibaba abetsimbi"
  57,17,"Manye mbu Nyasaye alamusinjia liloba nilimalile okhufwa, toto khubenoosiye ibimanyisio biefu khomunyoole okhupara"
  57,18,"Toto balia abobwatoto abasatsa nabakhasi, bewosinjia Nyasaye likofi lilayi, balimetelwakhwo muno, ne balinyoola Omurungo kwabuwani bwabu"
  57,19,"Ne balia basuubila Nyasaye nende Abarumwa bebe abo nibo abobwatoto, nende abaloli imbeli wa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, abo balinyoola omurongo kwabu nende obulafu bwabu, ne balia bakhaya, nibaingasia ebimanyisio biefu, abo nibo Abandu bomumulilo"
  57,20,"Manye mbu obulamu bwokhushialo nomubayo nende okhukalilisia, nende okhwirona nende okhwilaya mwinywe nende okhushilana khumiandu nende Abana, bili shinga ifula, yemimela chiabu chisangasia abalimi, mana chitse chiume chikalukhane namabuyu mana chibe amasakaria, ne mwikulu khuli neshinyasio nende obulesheli nende okhufuchililwa okhurula khu Nyasaye, ne obulamu bwokhushialo shinishiosi shiosi tawe halali omwikhoyo kwobubeyi"
  57,21,"Ilushile eshileshelo shia Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi, nende omukunda kwomwikulu uburakalafu bwakwo bulishinga oburakalafu bwo mwikulu nende eshialo, kwarecheshelwa Abasuubila Nyasaye nende Abarumwa bebe, etso nitso tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye yelesinjia owayenya, ne Nyasaye ali netsimbaasi tsinyinji"
  57,22,"Ne amasila kosikosi shimwakhanyoola khushialo nohomba mwinywe halali khwamala okhubandichila mushitabu ,nikhushiili okhubaloonga, toto ako khu Nyasaye ni amangu"
  57,23,"Khomukhaye okhubeelela khushikorere mwinywe, ne mukhaye okhwilola khushiabahelesiye ne Nyasaye shiyachama ulia wibulisinjia ni yelola tawe"
  57,24,"Balia bemananga ne balomesinjia Abandu okhuba abeemani, ne ulia ukhaya amanye mbu Nyasaye niye Omuyinda Owitsomibwa muno"
  57,25,"Ne toto khwaruma Abarumwa befu nende bimanyisio binoosia, ne nikhubeshilia eshitabu nende eshichelo, kho Abandu beme khubwatoto, ne nikhwishia eshichuma shia amani amanji nende obukhoonyi khubandu, kho Nyasaye amanye ni wina umuhabina nende Abarumwa bebe khumakhuwa kefisile, toto Nyasaye niwa Amani Omushili muno"
  57,26,"Ne toto khwaruma Nuhu nende Ibrahim mana nikhura mulwibulo lwabu oburumwa nende eshitabu, mana khuli nende abasuubila mubo, ne abaanji mubo ni abakori"
  57,27,"Mana nikhubalondiakhwo Abarumwa abaanji inyuma wabu, ne nikhulondiakho Yesu Omwana wa Mariam, ne nikhumuwa injili, ne nikhura mumioyo chiabaloondi be eshisanendetsimbabaasi, nende“ obusirasoti” abeene nibo bachachia, sikhwa balachila ako tawe, halali okhukonya tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, halali shibaalondanga kenyekhana tawe. Mana balia basuubila mubo khwabawa omurungo kwabu, ne abanji mubo nabonooni"
  57,28,"Enywe abasuubila rie Nyasaye ne musuubile Omurumwa wuwe, yetsa akhubahelesia emikabo chibili mutsimbaasi tsie, ne alabahelesia obulafu bwokhuchendela, ne alabaleshela naye Nyasaye ni Omunji Owetsimbabaasi"
  57,29,"Kho Abandu beshitabu bamanye mbu babula obunyali khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, ne tsimbabaasi tsiosi tsili mumukhono kwa Nyasaye ahelesinjia owayenya, Ne Nyasaye niwetsimbasi tsinyinji"